25 final date of harvest.
26 (b) “Lot” means:
27 (1) The flowers from one or more cannabis plants of the
28 same harvest batch, in a quantity that weighs 15 pounds or less;
29 (2) The leaves or other plant matter from one or more
30 cannabis plants of the same harvest batch, other than full female
31 flowers, in a quantity that weighs 45 pounds or less; or
32 (3) The wet flower, leaves or other plant matter from one or
33 more cannabis plants of the same harvest batch used only for
